data.description: Well maintained home affording a fabulous water view from rear patio or deck while enjoying the freshly groomed yard. Concrete retaining wall with stamped patio and fencing finishes the look! Fish or paddleboat from your back yard. Open kitchen featuring granite and stainless appliances. New carpet and hardwood floors. Primary bedroom is conveniently located on main level with ensuite bath. Cozy fireplace in den only needs the Christmas stockings to be complete for the season! Wellington neighborhood amenities include clubhouse, playground, Jr. Olympic size pool, and 24 hour fitness center.
